data.description: Beautiful move-in ready townhome in Smyrna with upgrades throughout! Enter to the main level with gorgeous hardwood floors throughout. Entry and formal dining room feature chair railing accents and tons of natural light. The bright and open living room features a cozy fireplace and wall of windows with balcony access. Open concept kitchen has on-trend light fixtures as well as granite counters, stone backsplash, spacious breakfast bar, and butlers pantry. A breakfast room is attached as well as a keeping room that would make a great seating area to curl up with a good book or even a home office space! Upstairs, retreat to the oversized primary suite with a tray ceiling and en-suite bath with dual sinks, vanity seating, separate tub, glassed-in shower, and HUGE walk-in closer with a built-in closet system. Second bedroom on the top level has an en-suite bath. Don't miss the built-in desk space in the hallway as well as the convenience of an upstairs laundry room! There's even more space to spread out on the first level with an extra-large room - game room, media room, guest suite, man cave, you name it! Complete with a wet bar with room for a wine fridge, you'll never want to leave this space! A full bath is just steps away. Enjoy a large garage with storage space and outside fenced in green space with a covered patio. Extra touches like wrought iron stair spindles, high ceilings, and crown molding make this a dreamy home. Just minutes from all the charm Smyrna has to offer!
